{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Eggs, we didn't see them anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And another thing-- it was really very, very dangerous for a-- and then with this bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, they would announce that those bakeries are going to have bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So either my sister or I-- and this was when the anti-Semitism came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We would get up at 2 o'clock at night, you know, to get to the line, [INAUDIBLE] those bakeries that might have bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they started maybe selling at 6:00 in the morning, and the line was getting longer and longer and longer, and you were standing there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, after all this, one of-- the-- the-- of course, Germans were watching you look.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and then suddenly, one of the Poles would went-- would go to this German and start, you know, pointing out who he thinks is a Jew the line.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they would throw you out of the line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You went home without the piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was black.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, it was like clay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that is one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And secondly, my brothers, my father once-- you simply could not get out of the house, because they would be immediately grab you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you never knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some, maybe they killed and they never came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My family at that time, fortunately-- but they would grab you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would take you to wash all the latrines, latrines-- Latrines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Latrines.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For eight hours maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you would come back filthy and dirty, and sometimes bleeding because you didn't work fast enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another thing was, which I remember because it also pertained to-- to women, you went out-- so mostly the boys were staying home.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
